866
00:50:33.004 --> 00:50:34.784
metabolites in their TCA cycle.

867
00:50:35.704 --> 00:50:39.564
So this built a foundation for us. We took a cell line

868
00:50:39.604 --> 00:50:43.544
like MiaPaCa. We rationalized that if a cell line is known to be glycolytic,

869
00:50:43.764 --> 00:50:47.724
