00:54:02.544 --> 00:54:06.464
It's almost four times higher in the tumor, the levels of glutamine when we

926
00:54:06.524 --> 00:54:10.384
administer ketogenic diet. So we ask, what is the main source of the glutamine?

927
00:54:10.484 --> 00:54:13.924
Where is glutamine coming from? For the first round of experiment, we did a series

928
00:54:13.964 --> 00:54:17.484
of isotope tracing using glucose labels, ketone body

