00:54:44.344 --> 00:54:46.564
glutamine. So glutamine has to come from somewhere else.

938
00:54:47.204 --> 00:54:51.134
Through our collaboration with MacArthur Laboratory at Harvard, we observed that

939
00:54:51.164 --> 00:54:54.884
when we reduce the amount of protein in the diet, going from 20%

940
00:54:54.924 --> 00:54:58.724
protein to 10% to 6%, every increment of

941
00:54:58.764 --> 00:55:02.284
reduction in... dietary protein, we have

942
00:55:02.344 --> 00:55:05.464
