00:55:05.504 --> 00:55:08.904
produces and puts into the blood. So there is a glutamine

944
00:55:08.944 --> 00:55:12.914
recycling in the liver during the ketogenic diet, and this glutamine that

945
00:55:12.944 --> 00:55:16.504
we see in the tumor, four times higher, is probably coming from the

946
00:55:16.564 --> 00:55:20.544
liver. So what we did next is that we know that glutamine is coming from the

947
00:55:20.584 --> 00:55:24.024
